character.name: Xiao Long
character.concept:
Path of the Wheel - Path of the Steward
Elven Magic Face who utilizes Summoning and Physical Illusion based Spellcasting
character.notes:
Combat - Spirit of Earth - 11 phys def, 22 DR, Binding, Guard, [Concealment], [Engulf], [Elemental Attack]
Detection - Guidance
Health - Spirit of Air - 16 phys def, 12 DR, Concealment, Engulf, Movement, [Elemental Attack], [Fear]
Illusion - Water
Manipulation - Fire

Spirit of Man - 15 phys def, 19 DR, Concealment, Enhanced Senses, Guard, Influence. [Innate Spell], [Fear]

contact.name: Caduceus Lin
contact.notes: A Vietnamese with a flair for the nostalgic, he is usually found around "A Little Bit O' Saigon" amongst a larger community of Vietnamese.

contact.name: Jaun the Dicer
contact.notes: [Jaun] the [Dice]r - named after the disease he exhibits: jaundice. He is a ghoul taxi driver that is all too happy to get you where you need to go. His services are good, but they cost an arm and a leg. Really.

contact.name: Alexandria Der'Tanyot
contact.notes: Alexandria "Der'Tanyot" (DAIR TON-Yoht) is a talismonger on the edge of Downtown Seattle, where the riff raff from the suburbs and the seedy and needy underbelly can find her shop easily. She's got to make money, right? Purr, darling, purr.

contact.name: Terry Morris
contact.notes:
"Terry has an obligation to his family and the precinct. That doesn't mean that Terry can survive on his salary alone. Terry's got to look out for his family!"

- Terry

contact.name: Jaqi Dregburner
contact.notes: Jaqi is scary for her height, because she knows how to swing her width. Her knowledge of "hot" items is immense.

contact.name: Cillian O'Dreary
contact.notes: Owner of Dante's Inferno. Watches everything that goes on in his club.

contact.name: Loren Starsong
contact.notes: A moonlighting street doc that works at the Body+Health+Spirit Health Clinic as a day job.

contact.name: Kyle Turner
contact.notes:
Kyle can provide credentials to get into restricted access areas where press is allowed.

Xiao has known Kyle for a long time through gaming and college.

contact.name: Jackson "Hide" Covacs
contact.notes:
"Everyone looks down on us, but no one looks AT us. That's why we're able to smuggle anything we want. When the time is right, the Gnomes will rule this city from beneath!"

- Jackson "Hide" Covacs, when you specifically didn't ask about how he came about his latest shipment of slime-covered crates
